<paragraph blockId="46.[151,1436,1831,2037]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
Tribe 
<taxonomicName box="[217,362,1831,1856]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Platythyreini">Platythyreini</taxonomicName>
contains the single genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Roger. These" authorityName="Roger. These" authorityYear="1863" box="[654,938,1831,1856]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Platythyrea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[654,784,1831,1856]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Platythyrea</emphasis>
Roger. These
</taxonomicName>
ants are notable for their arboreal habits and frequent (probably nearly universal) presence of gamergate workers.
</paragraph>
